---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<style>
  h1 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: white;
    font-size: 2rem;
  }

  .legal-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    color: #ccc;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  h2 {
    color: white;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
  }
</style>

<MainLayout title="Legal">
  <h1>Legal & Policies</h1>
  <div class="legal-container">
    <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>We do not collect or share personal data without your explicit consent. If you subscribe to our newsletter, your email will be stored securely and never sold or shared.</p>

    <h2>Terms of Use</h2>
    <p>All content on this website is for informational and expressive purposes. You may share or quote it with proper attribution. Commercial use of our content without permission is not allowed.</p>

    <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
    <p>All images, texts, and graphics belong to UNHOLY101 unless otherwise stated. Respect creators. When in doubt, ask.</p>

    <h2>Freedom Comes With Respect</h2>
    <p>We stand for freedom of speech, but not for hate speech. Comments or messages that promote hate, exclusion, or harassment may be removed. Our platform is sacred to dignity.</p>
  </div>
</MainLayout>